  <scopecontent audience="internal" id="aspace_eb28e766fed13dda0df1bbbf1fa6acd3">
    <head>Scope and content</head>
<p>Cornell Class of 1912 items include scrapbooks of clippings, photographs, programs (including Class Day program), menus, poetry, songs, and correspondence (1908-12); printed material; alumni photographs and negatives; reunion scrapbooks (1912-52) and clothing; a 1912 pillow case; and three Class of 1912 pins.</p>  </scopecontent>
  <scopecontent audience="internal" id="aspace_93179cd39533a01ed4ba3f8edf89fd8e">
    <head>Scope and content</head>
<p>Also, copies of the "On-to-Ithaca Gazette," 1930-1939.</p>  </scopecontent>
